:: Go meet up with Mr. White {"position":"500,1200","size":"100,100"}
Albuquerque morning already feels too bright.
(click: ?page)[==
Everything looks bleached out.
(click: ?page)[==
As you head toward your car, somebody yells:
(click: ?page)[==
“Yo! Pinkman!”
(click: ?page)[==
Normally someone shouting your last name out here means you're about to get popped, but that voice...
(click: ?page)[==
Combo is standing half out the window of his car, grinning like an idiot.

