:: Honestly? {"position":"600,775","size":"100,100"}
“Yeah, I’ve tried to stop before.”
(click: ?page)[==
“...really…”
(click: ?page)[==
“Actually, man, you’re making me remember this funny story.”
(click: ?page)[==
You take a long drag on the joint. 
(click: ?page)[==
No matter how many times you do it, the smoke still just kind of feels wrong sliding down your throat. 
(click: ?page)[==
Like you’re breaking a rule.
(click: ?page)[==
I like this feeling somedays, but somedays it’s just another boring thing about my life.


